<h1>No Caster Balance update</h1>
	Well, that sure is a crummy subject for a post...   <IMG SRC="http://boards.station.sony.com/ubb/everquest/smile.gif"><P><B>Hi Alan,<P>As a wizzy-int-caster type of fellow, I'd very much like to know what ever happened to the "caster balance" that was to happen.  Ive seen it on a few boards that you have done all you intend to do already.  If those few little changes we've seen to date are everything, I am underwhelmed.<P>Say it aint so! When is my "hopelessly outclassed in damage and easily killed in combat" wizzy gonna get a break?<P>Andrael Arcaenuemrunner<BR>22 levels and a couple of staffs<BR>Norath.</B><P>I would hold off on believing any rumors about us being finished with the caster balance thing until you read about it here.  Those EQ players just love to gossip!   <IMG SRC="http://boards.station.sony.com/ubb/everquest/smile.gif"><P>And Id argue pretty strongly against your words ...few little changes weve seen to date...  Some rather significant ideas have already been introduced into the game.<P>This isnt exactly a simple process (despite what some pundits would have you believe).  There are a lot of comparisons to make, much data to gather and plenty of ideas to toss out.  Its just gonna take some time, so please be patient.<P>Alan<BR>



